Springtown High School
March 5 at 8:23 PM ·

Porcupine Tennis Report for 3/5

Congratulations to the following Porcupine tennis medals winners: John Glover/Chloe Rich, gold medals in Mixed Doubles;
Adam Armstrong/Sydnee Burdzilauskas, silver medals in Mixed Doubles;
Halle Hughes/Autumn Walker, silver medals in Girls Doubles;
Malorie Henneck/Tori Tabor, Consolation Girls Doubles Title/bronze medals;
and Jayden Badillo/Samina Uddin, winning the Consolation Mixed Doubles Title to earn bronze medals.

Keep it up, Porcupines!

